  "summary": "Malicious code in chai-assertions-plus (npm)",
  "details": "Combosquat package impersonating the chai assertion library. Ships a file (lib/initializeCaller.js) containing an immediately-invoked async function that decodes a base64-embedded URL (hxxps://tomato-brunhilda-40[.]tiiny[.]site/index[.]json), fetches its contents via HTTP GET with a custom header (x-secret-key: _), and executes the response body as JavaScript code via the Function constructor with access to Node.js require, enabling arbitrary remote code execution on the installer's machine.",
